casebody.data:
Northwest Ohio Bar Association v. Archer.

[Cite as Northwest Ohio Bar Assn. v. Archer (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 97.]

(No. 93-453 Submitted April 20, 1993 Decided August 11, 1993.) *98Barber, Kaper, Stamm & Robinson and Jeffrey L Robinson, for relator. Stephen R. Archer, pro se. Per Curiam.

We agree with the findings and recommendation of the board and publicly reprimand respondent. Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
